&lt;div&gt;We are TRADER, a Canadian leader in digital automotive solutions. Our flagship brands — &lt;strong&gt;AutoTrader.ca&lt;/strong&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;AutoSync&lt;/strong&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Dealertrack Canada and CMS&lt;/strong&gt; — help Canadians buy, sell, and finance vehicles with confidence.&amp;nbsp;As part of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;AutoScout24 group&lt;/strong&gt;, Europe’s largest online car marketplace, we’re shaping the future of automotive retail in Canada and beyond.&lt;/div&gt;
