&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We are looking for a high-performing &lt;strong&gt;Matador&amp;nbsp;AI Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to drive revenue growth in the automotive sector. This role focuses on selling AI-powered solutions to dealerships and dealer groups, helping them improve sales performance, customer engagement, and operational efficiency.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;You will own the full sales cycle, act as a trusted advisor to automotive decision-makers, and translate AI capabilities into tangible business outcomes.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul data-end=&quot;1640&quot; data-start=&quot;799&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Own and manage the&amp;nbsp;full sales cycle: prospecting, discovery, demo, negotiation, and close&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Sell&amp;nbsp;AI-driven solutions&amp;nbsp;(e.g. conversational AI, lead management, broadcast) to automotive clients&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Build strong relationships with&amp;nbsp;dealer principals, general managers, sales directors, and stakeholders&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Identify customer pain points and position AI solutions that drive measurable ROI&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Develop and maintain a healthy pipeline through outbound prospecting and inbound leads&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
